# 🛒 Supermarket Billing System

A modern and simple **Supermarket Billing System** written in **C++**, designed for managing item inventories, generating bills, and tracking customer purchases. Built for use in local stores or as a learning project for aspiring developers.

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add and update inventory items  
- ✅ Support for multiple entries of the same item with different prices  
- ✅ Real-time billing with quantity checks  
- ✅ Customer bill generation with total amount  
- ✅ Admin login system *(optional enhancement)*  
- ✅ Customer details recording *(optional enhancement)*  
- ✅ Export bills for future reference  
- ✅ Console-based interface with clean user prompts

